data.description: SELLER WILL ALLOW A SELLER'S CONCESSION!!  Welcome to 740 E 242nd Street, a charming single-family haven nestled in the heart of the Bronx, NY 10470. This inviting residence boasts a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it an ideal home for those seeking a retreat in the city.  Featuring three spacious bedrooms, this home offers ample space for relaxation and personalization. The primary bedroom is a tranquil sanctuary, providing a peaceful escape at the end of the day. With two and a half bathrooms, morning routines and evening unwinding are made effortlessly convenient.  The warm and welcoming ambiance of the living spaces creates an inviting atmosphere for both family and guests. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with modern appliances and plenty of counter space for culinary endeavors. The adjacent dining area is perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories with loved ones.  One of the standout features of this property is the attached garage, providing both shelter for your vehicle and additional storage space. The convenience of a private driveway ensures parking is never a concern. The front and back patios offer delightful outdoor spaces for enjoying the fresh air, whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a summer barbecue.  Conveniently located in a sought-after neighborhood, this residence is in proximity to various amenities, including schools, parks, and shopping centers. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to public transportation and major thoroughfares.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 740 E 242nd Street your new home, where comfort, style, and convenience come together seamlessly.  SELLING AS IS.
